Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: what's my drug
des:
What's My Drug helps you find information about prescription drugs. Including whether it is a generic or not and what it is used for. You don't need to provide any information apart from the name of a medicine and it can tell you some things about it. Like whether it is a generic or the type of drug it is (e.g. "lipid lowering drugs"). it uses the official BNF codes and text used in other parts of the world too.

The information in this skill is provided for informational and educational purposes only. It is not a substitute for professional medical advice, treatment or diagnosis. Call your doctor to receive medical advice. If you think you may have a medical emergency, please dial your local emergency response phone number.
